## 9. Ask Vs Agent Decision Table

| Behavior | Ask | Agent |
|---|---:|---:|
| Direct answer bubble | yes | yes |
| Read workspace context | yes | yes |
| Show workspace analysis card | no | yes |
| Show tool activity card | no by default | yes |
| Run planner | no | yes |
| Show plan card | no | yes |
| Create to-do card | no | yes |
| Write files | no | permission/review flow |
| Run shell commands | no | permission flow |
| Create diff | no | yes |
| Review/apply changes | no | yes |
| Show read-only pill | yes | no |
| Show autonomy control | no | yes |

